quran[31{c,v,t}:
79,16,jab unn ke perwar-digaar ne un ko pak maidan ( yani ) tawee mein puraka
79,17,( aur hukum diya ) ke firaon ke paas jao woh sarkash ho raha hai
79,18,aur ( is se ) kaho kekiya to chahta hai ke pak ho jaye ?
79,19,aur mein tujhe tairay perwar-digaar ka rasta batau taakay tujh ko khauf ( peda ) ho
79,20,gharz unhon ne is ko barri nishani dikhayi
79,21,magar is ne jhatlaya aur nah maana
79,22,phir lout gaya aur tadbeerye karne laga
79,23,aur ( logon ko ) akhattakiya aur puraka
79,24,kehnay laga ke tumhara sab se bara maalik mein hon
79,25,to khuda ne is ko duniya aur akhirat ( dono ) ke azaab mein pakar liya
79,26,jo shakhs ( khuda se ) dar rakhta hai is ke liye is ( qissay ) mein Ibrat hai
79,27,bhala tumhara banana aasaan hai ya aasman ka? isi ne is ko banaya
79,28,is ki chhat ko ounchakiya aur phir usay barabar kar diya
79,29,aur isi ne raat ko tareek banaya aur ( din ko ) dhoop nikaali
79,30,aur is ke baad zameen ko phela diya
79,31,isi ne is mein se is ka pani nikala aur chara ugaya
79,32,aur is par pahoron kabojh rakh diya
79,33,yeh sab kuch tumahray aur tumahray charpayon ke faiday ke liye (kiya )
79,34,to jab barri aafat aeye gi
79,35,is din ensaan apne kamon ko yaad kere ga
79,36,aur dozakh dekhnay walay ke samnay nikaal kar rakh di jaye gi
79,37,to jis ne sar kashi ki
79,38,aur duniya ki zindagi ko muqaddam samgha
79,39,is ka thikana dozakh hai
79,40,aur jo apne perwar-digaar ke samnay kharray honay se darta aur jee ko khawahishon se rokta raha
79,41,is ka thikana bahisht hai
79,42,"( ae paighambar, log ) tum se qayamat ke baray mein puchhte hain ke is ka wuqoo kab ho ga ?"
79,43,so tum is ke zikar se kis fikar mein ho
79,44,is ka munhtaha ( yani waqay honay ka waqt ) tumahray perwar-digaar hi ko ( maloom hai )
79,45,jo shakhs is se dar rakhta hai tum to isi ko dar sunanay walay ho
79,46,jab woh is ko dekhen ge ( to aisa khayaal karen ge ) ke goya ( duniya mein sirf ) aik shaam ya subah rahay they
